{"tid":300912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立會三讀通過小巴座位上限增至19個","createTime":"2017-06-28T09:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T13:14:50.000Z","uid":48093,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9233a099db19a6b5774b90005f967002ca4adfb","tid":300912,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170628/photo/bkn-20170628165133244-0628_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170628172939\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170628%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170628165133244-0628_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170628172939&h=bbeca03a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會下午三讀通過《2017年道路交通(修訂)條例草案》，增加公共小巴座位的上限，由16個增至19個。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員尹兆堅早前撤回修正案，他今日在會上以恐怖分子手法作比喻，指政府是恐怖分子，以草案為人質作要脅，強迫他撤回其修訂。<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅早前曾提出修正案，把座位數目增至20個，最後指為了整體公眾利益而撤回。他今日在會上指出，政府曾作出承諾，指議員即使提出修訂，都不會撤回草案，但最終政府「賴貓」，揚言撤回草案。他形容是玉石俱焚、一拍兩散，嚴重破壞行政立法的關係。他又指，其實絕大多數議員均希望可爭取增加座位至20座，甚至技術上也可行。他表示，希望政府能信守承諾，在兩年間作檢討。<br />\n<br />\n議員陸頌雄表示，原則上支持有關方案，形容此乃有缺憾的方案。他批評，政府只回應僱主和乘客的需求，但未有就此改善小巴司機的薪酬和福利。議員劉國勳表示，若增加座位，能減少乘客的輪候時間。他又指，現時支持政府的方案，但希望政府能在明年立即作出檢討。"},{"pid":"a52d9dac5d177c10cb25a80f97f70f033b0705f9","tid":300912,"uid":68547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T09:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://z9x9.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/20160506_572cbb02236c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fz9x9.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F05%2F20160506_572cbb02236c7.jpg&h=cd864cbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c96119c91e793a08476a0ffdefbdb7655d9b313a","tid":300912,"uid":89743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T09:43:33.000Z","msg":"特區班垃圾唔知背後收咗幾多億<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac65d7bc250d630131111bfbe713167017c76ce","tid":300912,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c0c8672c25ebd7a343ebe397da9ce8fbfa677b","tid":300912,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:45:02.000Z","msg":"其實點加？"},{"pid":"f8688e90438fce401e83961c524e1302edf082f7","tid":300912,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:51:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點加？</blockquote><br />\n門隔離加一個？"},{"pid":"f14d34b6cc1b1b0ead355b61f81b3aeb52490e71","tid":300912,"uid":113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點加？</blockquote><br />\n有部分小巴你見到有行李位嘅，就可以加位"},{"pid":"5bb6ae15a2fa6ff540dbf9d52302c80f155e74b8","tid":300912,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實點加？</blockquote><br />\n有部分小巴你見到有行李位嘅，就可以加位</blockquote><br />\n啲位可以密D"},{"pid":"f864a273222786658823fac267f56d0fe1bc36fb","tid":300912,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=SLihxwXrK4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSLihxwXrK4A&d=XM9Y1UHZQHybt6cAtfxxePiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6d98d778\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=SLihxwXrK4A</a>"},{"pid":"a3a05baf78d329d55e6db13e43cd8571a24f93b1","tid":300912,"uid":78165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebaf5eed8b531cd4c729c039c175c6ab1785ac92","tid":300912,"uid":3068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"不如全部企位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e59bba19eab3f54ed2fd32bcd90ee3ced20db98","tid":300912,"uid":76398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"